name: VaporWaveV1
description:
This LoRa was trained on 63 different images. Most of them are classic vaporwave.

It likes to generate images of statues (which can be slightly NSFW). It also likes plants and of course pools, but should be capable of adding a vaporwave aesthetic or colorset to most subjects even if it could always be better.

Recommended strength: 0.7, with a CFG from 3.5 to 5.5, though your mileage may vary.

There's also some creepy Backrooms found footage style pool pictures in the training set as well, so if you're into that sort of thing you might find some use out of this LoRa for that kind of imagery as well (activate this with triggers like 'found footage', 'dark', 'slides'').
